$ VBA: datatype longPtr
@ longPtr

In a → development/languages/VBA/language/32-vs-64-bit[32-bit] Office environment, a `longPtr` is equivalent to a → development/languages/VBA/language/datatypes/long[`long`], in a 64-bit Office environment, it is equivalent
to a → development/languages/VBA/language/datatypes/longLong[`longLong`].

sa:

  → development/languages/VBA/language/32-vs-64-bit#vba_32_64_ptrSafe[`ptrSafe`]

